:

*Odlaziš* iz sobe (You are leaving the room).
Ona *odlazi* sama (She is leaving alone).
Njegov sin *odlazi* u školu (His son is going to school).
Niko se neće suprotstaviti kada *odlaziš* (Nobody will oppose when you leave).
Ona je rekla da *odlazi* odavde (She said she was leaving from here).
Već *odlaziš* kući? (Are you already leaving home?).